Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:35.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.80,0:01:43.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Johnny!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.47,0:01:45.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ow, ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.37,0:01:48.36,Font 1,,0,0,0,,A-Are you okay, Takizawa?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:51.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.74,0:01:56.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki! What happened to Osugi?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.18,0:01:58.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Osugi is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.81,0:02:04.81,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Actually, it looks like what\Nhappened was unrelated to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.76,0:02:11.19,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess I passed out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.19,0:02:15.53,Font 1,,0,0,0,,When you came to the hotel,\Nwas there anyone else there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.70,0:02:20.33,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.61,0:02:36.12,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(316,394)}Episode 8:\NSearching for the Path Already Lost
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.12,0:02:38.05,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(304,198)}Eden of the East
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.45,0:02:39.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There's something wrong with the fact
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:42.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,that you thought I was a Johnny\NHunter victim in the first place!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.89,0:02:48.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. But the SOS was\Nposted to that site you like, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:52.90,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Idiot! It's a secret that I use that site!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:56.37,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I would've listened to your\Nlove woes anytime you wanted...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.37,0:02:59.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, stop it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.47,0:03:04.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Anyway, you can't say that Kasuga's\Nmistake was completely unfounded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:08.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We couldn't get you on the phone,\Nand we saw a pic of that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.95,0:03:12.82,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Anybody would've thought you\Nwere the one calling for help.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sure, this is the bag I lost, but still,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.96,0:03:21.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,normal people'd think of other reasons\NI might not be answering the phone!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.23,0:03:24.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,The fact is, I was roped into a drinking party
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.00,0:03:26.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,on the pretense of\N"prospective employee training."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:31.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So they took your cell phone\Naway, huh? I hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:35.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But thank goodness. I'm so glad\Nyour johnny didn't get cut off!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.08,0:03:36.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.31,0:03:41.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,In other words, after you left Kasuga,\Nsomeone took your bag,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.48,0:03:44.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,then ran into the Johnny Hunter,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.69,0:03:51.29,Font 1,,0,0,0,,got trapped in the Hotel Insomnia,\Nand started sending out SOS's?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.29,0:03:54.70,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then Takky invaded the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.70,0:03:58.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But the Johnny Hunter was gone,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:02.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and all that remained were signs that\Nsomeone had been confined there.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(151,90)\fn\fs36}WORLD VIEW NEWS
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:03.17,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(197,232)}Explosion at Hotel Insomnia
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(208,85)}Signs Someone was Confined There
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:06.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(217,204)}Could it be the notorious "Johnny Hunter"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.24,0:04:08.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(246,213)}Connection to the Play-by-Play Posted\Nto a Certain Site Being Investigated
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.81,0:04:12.28,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Can I ask one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.28,0:04:16.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What relationship are we going\Nto have with this Takizawa now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.72,0:04:22.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I have to go drop by work now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.62,0:04:23.63,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(306,239)}Eden of the East
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.99,0:04:27.16,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Then I'm going to go pick up Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.16,0:04:31.83,Font 1,,0,0,0,,And if you guys are going to\Nteam up with this Takizawa guy,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:37.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but we'll probably\Nnever all meet like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.41,0:04:39.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:44.51,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Even I have my pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:46.24,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Osugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.68,0:04:50.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So, what now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.89,0:04:53.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I don't think he's a bad guy, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.72,0:04:56.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yes, he doesn't seem like a villain,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:59.49,Font 1,,0,0,0,,but the fact is, there are a lot\Nof strange things about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.49,0:05:03.60,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Like how he found that hotel all of a sudden,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.60,0:05:06.73,Font 1,,0,0,0,,and how he got out unchallenged afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.73,0:05:12.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I think it might be a good idea to\Nask him about things personally.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.61,0:05:14.41,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Sounds like he's coming soon anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You got a text from Saki? When?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.38,0:05:19.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Right before Osugi came.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.61,0:05:22.72,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He could be here any time now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.72,0:05:26.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I wonder if it was right for us to let Osugi go.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:36.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Saki...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.58,0:05:53.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Am I the only one who didn't know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.15,0:05:57.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.98,Font 1,,0,0,0,,--What's with him?\N--Creepy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.97,0:06:16.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(319,105)}Searching
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.91,0:06:20.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So he's not registered with Eden...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.78,0:06:22.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,105)}Taking Picture
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(163,115)}Comment
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.49,0:06:36.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(217,150)}Tell me who he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:45.66,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\pos(279,433)\fn\fs36}Selecao Activity History
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.44,0:06:50.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(285,189)}Destruction of evidence and prevention
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.34,0:06:53.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So she stopped the police for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.87,0:06:53.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,{\fn\fs36\pos(299,179)}of Police intervention at Hotel lnsomnia
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.88,0:06:57.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Am I the only one who doesn't\Nknow about the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.61,0:07:01.02,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I guess I'll have to read the old usage records...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.02,0:07:04.15,Font 1,,0,0,0,,So do you understand the\Nsituation with Osugi now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.15,0:07:05.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:10.96,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Good. So, there are a few\Nquestions we'd like to ask, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.96,0:07:14.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If it's about the registration,\Nwe can list me as the representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.80,0:07:16.30,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, that is one thing, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.30,0:07:20.97,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Even if something goes wrong down\Nthe line, I'll take full responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.97,0:07:25.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, but we can allot\Nrights and dividends equally.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.91,0:07:28.48,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're pretty generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:30.01,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.01,0:07:34.31,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Okay, then, I feel bad\Nasking this as a return favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.09,0:07:43.26,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But is there anyone who can fix this phone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.26,0:07:45.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I can't turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.00,0:07:53.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,There aren't even any holes\Nfor the charger to plug into.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.23,0:07:56.94,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Are there texts in here from before\Nyou lost your memory, or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.94,0:07:59.07,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.07,0:08:02.38,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Um, you had two of those phones?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.38,0:08:05.91,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Huh? oh, I found that one in the movie theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.91,0:08:09.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But I don't really know what's on it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.18,0:08:12.69,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Yeah, you don't even have\Nyour own memories, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.69,0:08:16.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What about it, Micchon? Can you fix it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:20.13,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Phones aren't like computers.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.13,0:08:21.80,Font 1,,0,0,0,,No luck, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:27.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Oh, I know. Maybe Itazu\Ncould do something with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.20,0:08:29.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Underpants, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.14,0:08:31.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,True, he might be able to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.87,0:08:33.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Who's this "Underpants" guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.88,0:08:39.95,Font 1,,0,0,0,,We got a lot of advice from him\Nwhen we were making the Eden site.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.95,0:08:45.55,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He's one of the best, hailed as\Nthe Whiz Kid of Kyoto, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:46.62,Font 1,,0,0,0,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:47.89,Font 1,,0,0,0,,For the last two years,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.89,0:08:50.79,Font 1,,0,0,0,,he's shut himself up in a little\Napartment on the Kamogawa River.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.79,0:08:53.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,They say he never even goes to school anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.30,0:08:58.67,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'm going to pay him a little visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.67,0:09:02.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You can go, but I don't think\Nhe'll be willing to see anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:06.14,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Why not? Sure he will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.14,0:09:08.68,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Hey. You're not even going to\Nask his address before you leave?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.68,0:09:11.34,Font 1,,0,0,0,,oh, you'll tell it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.08,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, take Micchon with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.08,0:09:19.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It'll up your chances of\Ngetting in the door a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.59,0:09:24.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,What? I don't want to! I hate Underpants!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.03,0:09:26.99,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Now, don't be like that. As a fellow programmer,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.99,0:09:31.03,Font 1,,0,0,0,,you're the only one of us who can\Nhold a decent conversation with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.03,0:09:36.04,Font 1,,0,0,0,,While you're at it, ask him if he's\Nfinished that World Computer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:38.27,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll text him a heads-up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.88,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll go,too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:46.61,Font 1,,0,0,0,,It's the same place he was living before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.32,0:09:58.23,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Will they be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.23,0:10:01.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Well, as spies, they're not very promising.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.20,0:10:03.00,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Spies?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:06.87,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You're curious about Takizawa's past too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:11.47,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If he's got texts from before his\Nmemory loss, don't you want to see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.47,0:10:14.18,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I get it. In that case, I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.18,0:10:16.84,Font 1,,0,0,0,,You can't get anything out of Underpants.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.84,0:10:21.52,Font 1,,0,0,0,,He may not look it, but Yutaka Itazu\Nhas a big soft spot for women.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.52,0:10:25.42,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Aren't all men that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.42,0:10:27.59,Font 1,,0,0,0,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.59,0:10:31.86,Font 1,,0,0,0,,I'll text Itazu and Micchon to that effect later.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.86,0:10:37.20,Font 1,,0,0,0,,While they're out, let's go over these\Ndocuments Takizawa brought again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.20,0:10:41.50,Font 1,,0,0,0,,If he's a con man, there should\Nbe holes in here somewhere.
